{"TopicId":158644,"ForumId":18,"TopicTitle":"Camera Obscura","CreatedByName":"Serpens Solidus","CreatedById":146847,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-04-03T15:43:08Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Serpens Solidus","CreatedById":146847,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-04-03T15:43:08Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhen the roller blinds in my room are almost closed, magical horizontal lines appear on the wall. I realized that those lines correspond to the horizontal features of the neighbor\u0027s house. This inspired me to convert my room to a camera obscura. For a long time, I was too lazy to actually do it. But I got bored yesterday, so I decided to put the idea to the test.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI improvised a pinhole using stuff lying around:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022J35s4YE.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022768\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/J35s4YE.jpg\u0022 width=\u00221024\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe result was pretty cool:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022QKJvcoa.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022768\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/QKJvcoa.jpg\u0022 width=\u0022576\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHere is an enhanced image for your viewing pleasure:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u002272HzyHe.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022768\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/72HzyHe.png\u0022 width=\u0022576\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt is quite fun to see people walk by upside down on the wall\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222017-04-03T20:41:52Z\u0022 title=\u002204/03/2017 08:41  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003EApril 3, 2017\u003C/time\u003E by Serpens Solidus\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003EEnhanced enhanced image\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Shpaget","CreatedById":45577,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-04-03T18:57:08Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHA! That\u0027s awesome!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis is the very first photo I took with my first film obscura I made from a cellphone box.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022xN1CkJK.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022698\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/xN1CkJK.jpg\u0022 width=\u00221024\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnyway, your room definitely qualifies for this:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022http://pinholeday.org\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttp://pinholeday.org\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Serpens Solidus","CreatedById":146847,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-04-03T19:17:26Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCool, but I don\u0027t feel like covering my room in photographic paper \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:P\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_tongue.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:P\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Shpaget","CreatedById":45577,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-04-03T19:25:10Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou don\u0027t need to!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe exact same technique you used for the photo above is just fine.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}